    <center><table class="itemDisplayTable">
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Title:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">A study on customer's buying intention towards Hybrid car in India at Ford India Pvt.Ltd.,</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Authors:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">Sakaravarthy M</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Keywords:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">buying intention</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Issue Date:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">1-May-2010 </td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Publisher:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">SRM University</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Series/Report no.:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">P4611</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">Abstract:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue">Eco-friendly vehicle helps in controlling emission of dangerous gases like carbon-dioxide and nitrous oxide they deliver better mileage than cars running on fossil fuel (Petrol&amp;Diesel). With rise in awareness of environmental pollution and its effects on the way of life, peopleâ€™s love for green cars has increased considerably over the past decade. Eco-friendly cars not only have a greener impact on nature but are also economical and it helps to save fast-depleting fossil fuels such as petrol and diesel. Car manufacturers have been going full swing to meet the changing scenario of consumer demands and have invested heavily on research and development of greener technologies for their cars.
The quality of CO2 released by a vehicle is basically proportional to the amount of fuel consumed; therefore fuel-efficient cars can definitely contribute to stop global warming. Compared to conventional cars, the hybrid car burn far less gas per mile and produce much less pollution, especially green house gases.
This study involves in making the customer aware about reasons for increasing environment pollution &amp; helping them to understand their role in decreasing it. The study also carries a process to analyze and understand a customer buying process.</td></tr>
<tr><td class="metadataFieldLabel">URI:&nbsp;</td><td class="metadataFieldValue"><a href="http://hdl.handle.net/123456789/8176">http://hdl.handle.net/123456789/8176</a></td></tr>
